  "description": "Single layer, fold amount at 0.08 — barely a fold. The waveform is almost unchanged; only the faintest trace of the second harmonic appears above the fundamental. The filter is closed to 0.22. What you hear is the ghost of a fold that never quite happened. An unwritten crease: the mark paper retains when you bend it almost but not quite enough.",
